        <header>
            <h1>Engineering Workshop Classes</h1>
            <p>B.Tech First Year | Building Future Engineers</p>
        </header>

        <div class="intro-section">
            <h2>About Workshop Training</h2>
            <p>Workshop practice is an essential component of engineering education that provides hands-on experience in various manufacturing and fabrication processes. For first-year B.Tech students, these workshops serve as a foundation to understand the practical aspects of engineering, bridging the gap between theoretical knowledge and real-world applications.</p>
            <p>Through these workshops, students gain exposure to different fields of engineering, develop manual skills, understand material properties, and learn safety protocols essential for any engineering professional.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="workshops-grid">
            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565193566173-7a0ee3dbe261?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Foundry Shop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Foundry Shop</h3>
                    <p>Learn the art of metal casting and pattern making. Students work with molten metals to create complex shapes and components.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Sand casting techniques</li>
                        <li>Pattern making and molding</li>
                        <li>Metal melting and pouring</li>
                        <li>Casting defects and remedies</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534398079543-7ae6d016b86a?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Carpentry Shop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Carpentry Shop</h3>
                    <p>Master woodworking skills and learn various joining techniques. Understanding wood as an engineering material and its applications.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Wood types and properties</li>
                        <li>Hand tools and power tools</li>
                        <li>Joinery techniques</li>
                        <li>Pattern and model making</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504328345606-18bbc8c9d7d1?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Sheet Metal Shop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Sheet Metal Shop</h3>
                    <p>Work with thin metal sheets to create various products through cutting, bending, and forming operations.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Sheet metal cutting and shearing</li>
                        <li>Bending and folding operations</li>
                        <li>Riveting and joining methods</li>
                        <li>Product development techniques</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092160562-40aa08e78837?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Welding Shop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Welding Shop</h3>
                    <p>Explore various welding techniques and learn to join metals permanently through fusion processes.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Arc welding fundamentals</li>
                        <li>Gas welding techniques</li>
                        <li>Safety procedures and equipment</li>
                        <li>Welding defects inspection</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092918056-0c4c3acd3789?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Machine Shop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Machine Shop</h3>
                    <p>Gain hands-on experience with machine tools like lathe, milling, and drilling machines for precision manufacturing.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Lathe operations and turning</li>
                        <li>Milling and drilling processes</li>
                        <li>Precision measurement tools</li>
                        <li>CNC machine introduction</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092918484-8313e1f7f467?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Fitting Shop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Fitting Shop</h3>
                    <p>Learn assembly operations and develop skills in filing, chipping, and precision fitting of components.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Hand tools operations</li>
                        <li>Filing and chipping techniques</li>
                        <li>Assembly and fitting practices</li>
                        <li>Threading and tapping</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092160607-ee22621dd758?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Smithy Shop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Smithy Shop (Forging)</h3>
                    <p>Experience traditional blacksmithing and metal forging techniques to shape metals through heating and hammering.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Forging operations</li>
                        <li>Hot and cold working of metals</li>
                        <li>Tool making and hardening</li>
                        <li>Metal heat treatment basics</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="workshop-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092162384-8987c1d64718?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Electronics Workshop" class="workshop-image">
                <div class="workshop-content">
                    <h3>Electronics Workshop</h3>
                    <p>Introduction to electronic components, circuit assembly, and basic troubleshooting techniques.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>PCB soldering and assembly</li>
                        <li>Electronic components identification</li>
                        <li>Circuit testing and debugging</li>
                        <li>Basic project development</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
